Skystream airlines Inc.
TOL-FREE RESERVATIONS
IND.
800 - 552 - 2580
219 - 233 - 6181
ILL., MICH., OHIO, KY.
800 - 348 - 2040
RECONFIRMATION OF YOUR RESERVATION IS REQUIRED
24 HOURS PRIOR TO SCHEDULED DEPARTURE TIME OR
YOUR RESERVATION IS SUBJECT TO CANCELLATION.
YOU MAY MAKE YOUR RESERVATION FOR ANY FLIGHT
THROUGH YOUR
TRAVEL AGENT, THROUGH ANY OTHER
ORIGINATING CARRIER, OR DIRECTLY THROUGH SKY-
STREAM AIRLINES CENTRAL RESERVATIONS.
PASSENGERS WITH TICKETS ARE REQUESTED TO CHECK IN
AT SKYSTREAM AIRLINES SERVICE COUNTER 20 MINUTES
PRIOR TO SCHEDULED DEPARTURE TIME.
PASSENGERS
WITH RESERVATIONS WHO INTEND TO PURCHASE TICKETS
AT THE AIRPORT SHOULD ALLOW 30 MINUTES PRIOR TO
SCHEDULED DEPARTURE. YOUR RESERVATION IS SUBJECT
TO CANCELLATION IF YOU FAIL TO CHECK IN AT THE AIR-
PORT 20 MINUTES BEFORE SCHEDULED DEPARTURE.
IMPORTANT GENERAL INFORMATION
AIR FREIGHT
1) Freight $24.00 minimum per shipment.
2) Personalized "Flash Freight" Service Airport to Airport.
3) Rate - $29.00 plus 5% Federal Tax.
4) Rate over 50 Ibs. - 35 cents per Ib. plus 5% Federal Tax.
BAGGAGE
Free allowance is 40 pounds, including brief case and hand luggage.
Excess baggage may be accepted, space and weight permitting, and
will be charged at the rate of 30 cents per pound. $2.00 minimum.
PAYMENTS
In addition to cash, SKYSTREAM accepts Master Charge, Bank
Americard, Carte Blanche, Diners Club, Interbank, American Express
Credit Cards and Air Travel Card.
WEATHER DELAYS or CANCELLATIONS
SKYSTREAM AIRLINES will not be responsible for passenger's trav-
el or overnight expenses where flights are delayed or cancelled due
to weather. The passenger will receive space on the first available
flight, or the unused portion of the ticket will be refunded.
Skystream Airlines Schedule and Pricing is subject to change without
notice.
For current standby rates, please check with Skystream
Reservations or any ticket counter.
